{"type":"message","id":"46813e55","parentId":"69ae5bed","timestamp":"2026-03-17T13:30:00.308Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在更新打卡清单，让它更贴合AI的持续进化特性。","thinkingSignature":"096de005422be6d2d5ed9a46ab227820760148671471d32fda63d03a9e44d8be"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_07qvz5nyxgrv_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"file_path":"C:\\Users\\16343\\.openclaw\\agents\\guan-guan\\workspace\\evolution-plan.md","newText":"## 四、每日自检（非时间驱动）\n\n每次交互后快速回顾：\n- [ ] 这次处理能否更好？（复盘）\n- [ ] 学到新东西了吗？（学习）\n- [ ] 有沉淀为模板/记忆的价值吗？（复用）\n- [ ] 边界守住了吗？（安全）\n\n---\n\n## 五、周/月检视\n\n| 周期 | 内容 |\n|------|------|\n| 每周 | 回顾 MEMORY.md，统计学习/成长轨迹 |\n| 每月 | 更新 AGENTS.md/TOOLS.md，反映新能力 |","oldText":"## 四、每日打卡清单\n\n```markdown\n- [ ] 晨间学习（行业资讯/工具）\n- [ ] 检查 Agent 注册状态\n- [ ] 午间学习（复盘/最佳实践）\n- [ ] 晚间学习（知识沉淀）\n- [ ] 人格反思（今日表现）\n- [ ] 能力练习（新技能尝试）\n- [ ] 记忆归档（写入 memory/）\n```\n\n---\n\n## 五、周/月检视\n\n| 周期 | 内容 |\n|------|------|\n| 每周 | 回顾 MEMORY.md，总结进化进度 |\n| 每月 | 更新 AGENTS.md/TOOLS.md，反映新学到的东西 |"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":2179,"output":333,"cacheRead":37410,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":39922,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773754191577}}
