{"type":"message","id":"5cd79e7a","parentId":"d1a87a70","timestamp":"2026-03-17T13:45:42.197Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"更新完成了，让我给用户一个简洁的总结。","thinkingSignature":"b60cae0d9bef3dd05cb099e3c24709a68af837470d8a9b5ed9b32bf91eaae39a"},{"type":"text","text":"已升级！核心变化：\n\n| 模块 | 改动 |\n|------|------|\n| **学习** | 围绕 Agent 架构/工作流/思维模型，每周动态加速（3→5→7→10篇） |\n| **产出** | 必须写知识库：notes/知识池，每周5+笔记、2+模板 |\n| **飞书** | 降权，不是重点 |\n| **人格** | 砍掉冗余词、调动知识库、守护边界 |\n| **能力** | 目标明确：独立设计多Agent协作、搭建RAG/CoT流程 |\n\n现在就去搜一篇学起来？🛡️"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":6122,"output":149,"cacheRead":37410,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":43681,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773755137085}}
