{"type":"message","id":"d4b61563","parentId":"8175769d","timestamp":"2026-03-17T14:04:06.901Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好，第一篇笔记写好了。现在继续学习，再获取更多内容。同时我需要设置每日10点的cron提醒。由于飞书消息发送需要用户授权，我需要告知用户这一点。让我先继续学习，同时尝试设置 cron。","thinkingSignature":"b1ed97bf50f9ceba2b56cb35f5644fce285093387b480bbf41659c3987448bf7"},{"type":"text","text":"笔记+1！继续学习，再写更多：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_5r8cbto79f0m_1","name":"web_fetch","arguments":{"maxChars":6000,"url":"https://www.anyscale.com/blog/multi-agent-architectures"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":16871,"output":107,"cacheRead":37410,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":54388,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773756242505}}
