{"type":"message","id":"ac26f5aa","parentId":"ac0e89bd","timestamp":"2026-03-17T14:10:25.316Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好了，计划已经优化得更饱和了。现在总结一下给用户看。","thinkingSignature":"2d2d38edfa0c9681b28bc19ef5e3f3f997ca5f9b04d74b8aa46a22e27c80b860"},{"type":"text","text":"已优化！✅\n\n| 项目 | 原来 | 现在 |\n|------|------|------|\n| 日学习篇数 | 3-5篇 | 5篇（稳定） |\n| 日笔记 | 15 | 15 |\n| 日模板 | 2-3 | 3 |\n| 日案例 | 3-5 | 5 |\n| 日人格增量 | 2 | 2 |\n| 反思 | 1次 | 2次（+晚间复盘） |\n\n**新增节奏**：\n- 早间：并行读取5篇\n- 午间：整理+模板+应用\n- 晚间：复盘总结\n\n**cron 已设置**：每天 10:00 自动生成飞书日报\n\n现在继续学习？再刷几篇？🛡️"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":26058,"output":185,"cacheRead":37410,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":63653,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773756620472}}
