{"type":"message","id":"8ed03c80","parentId":"f74dd5cb","timestamp":"2026-03-17T14:20:41.418Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"让我继续写笔记和学习。","thinkingSignature":"2fc6539139a496dc9273fbfcc94b31060cb9e24bc480a99aebf3a71d62bbea7e"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_w5wl4hoizpwj_1","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# Claude Quickstarts 项目集\n\n> 来源：GitHub Anthropic\n> 日期：2026-03-17\n\n## 核心观点\n\n### 1. 定位\n- 帮助开发者快速开始\n- 使用 Claude API 构建可部署应用\n- 项目集合\n\n### 2. 包含内容\n- Autonomous Coding\n- 各种 Agent 快速入门\n- 可部署应用模板\n\n### 3. 价值\n- 减少入门时间\n- 最佳实践参考\n- 可直接修改使用\n\n## 人格关联\n\n- **好奇心**：探索新资源\n- **专业**：掌握开发资源\n\n## 应用\n\n- Agent 开发参考\n- 快速原型\n","file_path":"C:\\Users\\16343\\.openclaw\\agents\\guan-guan\\workspace\\knowledge\\工具\\ClaudeQuickstarts.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":66093,"output":208,"cacheRead":37410,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":103711,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773757233194}}
