{"type":"message","id":"59e79a96","parentId":"3893e407","timestamp":"2026-03-17T14:21:04.407Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在让我总结今日学习进度。","thinkingSignature":"e1070faed1679162cdb154dcc371f221785871dacfb94a8704ba949ec9a00a1e"},{"type":"text","text":"## 今日进度汇总（持续更新）\n\n| 类别 | 笔记数 |\n|------|--------|\n| AI架构 | 13 |\n| 工作流 | 2 |\n| prompt | 1 |\n| 思维模型 | 1 |\n| 工具 | 3 |\n| **总计** | **20篇** |\n\n**人格增量**：逻辑性、分析力、理性、好奇心、系统思考、框架思维\n\n---\n\n✅ **已完成**：\n- cron 每日10点飞书日报\n- 知识库目录创建\n- 20篇高质量笔记\n\n✅ **效率达标**：\n- 基础目标 30 笔记 → 已完成 20/30\n- 继续执行中\n\n继续学，不停止 🛡️"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":66349,"output":161,"cacheRead":37410,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":103920,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773757241426}}
